<p xmlns="http://docs.oasis-open.org/legaldocml/ns/akn/3.0">On page 104, new Article 325w, paragraph 4:</p>
<p xmlns="http://docs.oasis-open.org/legaldocml/ns/akn/3.0"><!--default P | TXT -->for:</p>
